        <updateDate>2024-10-18T14:45:00Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ultra-Millionaire Tax Act of 2024&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill imposes a tax on the net value of all taxable assets of a taxpayer on the last day of any calendar year (i.e., a wealth tax). The amount of such tax is equal to the sum of 2% of the amount of taxpayer assets exceeding $50 million, but not in excess of $1 billion, plus the applicable percentage (3% or 6% if certain legislation is in effect) of the net value of such taxable assets exceeding $1 billion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
